### Sprint 1: Message Broker (RabbitMQ) - Testes de Integração

### 1. Health Check Geral do Sistema
GET http://localhost:8000/readyz
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Health Check do RabbitMQ
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tasks/health/rabbitmq
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Adicionar Experiências para Teste (Memória Episódica)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/memory/experience
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "O sistema detectou que o Circuit Breaker do Neo4j foi acionado 3 vezes em 5 minutos. Isso indica possível problema de conectividade com o banco de dados.",
  "type": "system_monitoring",
  "metadata": {
    "component": "Neo4j",
    "circuit_breaker_state": "OPEN",
    "failures": 3,
    "timestamp": "2025-10-06T15:00:00Z"
  }
}

###

### 4. Adicionar Mais Experiências
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/memory/experience
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Implementado novo padrão de resiliência usando retries com backoff exponencial. O LLM Manager agora tenta 3 vezes antes de falhar, com intervalos de 1s, 2s e 4s.",
  "type": "architecture_improvement",
  "metadata": {
    "pattern": "exponential_backoff",
    "component": "LLM Manager",
    "max_retries": 3,
    "timestamp": "2025-10-06T15:05:00Z"
  }
}

###

### 5. Publicar Tarefa de Consolidação (Modo Batch) via RabbitMQ
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tasks/consolidation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mode": "batch",
  "limit": 5
}

###

### 6. Verificar Fila de Consolidação
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tasks/queue/janus.knowledge.consolidation
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Publicar Tarefa de Consolidação (Modo Single)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tasks/consolidation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mode": "single",
  "experience_id": "test-exp-123",
  "experience_content": "O Prometheus está coletando métricas de todos os componentes críticos do sistema: LLM requests, memory operations, database queries e circuit breaker states.",
  "metadata": {
    "component": "Prometheus",
    "metrics_count": 45,
    "timestamp": "2025-10-06T15:10:00Z"
  }
}

###

### 8. Aguardar Processamento e Verificar Fila Novamente (após ~10s)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tasks/queue/janus.knowledge.consolidation
Accept: application/json

###

### 9. Verificar Entidades Criadas no Grafo
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/system/query-graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "MATCH (n) WHERE n:TECHNOLOGY OR n:PATTERN OR n:CONCEPT RETURN labels(n)[0] as type, n.name as name, n.last_seen ORDER BY n.last_seen DESC LIMIT 20"
}

###

### 10. Verificar Relacionamentos Criados
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/system/query-graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "MATCH (a)-[r]->(b) WHERE NOT a:Experience RETURN type(r) as relationship, a.name as from, b.name as to LIMIT 20"
}

###

### 11. Publicar Múltiplas Tarefas em Paralelo
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tasks/consolidation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mode": "batch",
  "limit": 3
}

###

POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tasks/consolidation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mode": "batch",
  "limit": 2
}

###

### 12. Verificar Profundidade da Fila
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tasks/queue/janus.knowledge.consolidation
Accept: application/json

###

### 13. Métricas Prometheus - Message Broker
GET http://localhost:8000/metrics
Accept: text/plain

# Buscar por:
# - message_broker_published_total
# - message_broker_consumed_total
# - message_broker_latency_seconds
# - message_broker_queue_depth
# - message_broker_active_consumers

###

### 14. Estatísticas do RabbitMQ Management UI
### Abrir navegador: http://localhost:15672
### User: janus
### Password: janus_pass

###

### 15. Verificar Experiências Consolidadas
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/system/query-graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "MATCH (e:Experience) WHERE e.consolidated_at IS NOT NULL RETURN e.id, e.type, e.timestamp, e.consolidated_at ORDER BY e.consolidated_at DESC LIMIT 10"
}

###

### 16. Buscar Experiências por Padrão Detectado
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/system/query-graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "MATCH (p:PATTERN)<-[:MENTIONS]-(e:Experience) RETURN p.name, count(e) as mentions ORDER BY mentions DESC"
}

###

